{"tid":1657662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[打倒昨日的我] 一月林鄭先話未有計劃調整按揭成數","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:54:32.000Z","uid":38864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"608fb6c2285f8c8fa2a331523f7195baa45c2611","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:45:56.000Z","msg":"Source: Twitter (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/alvinllum/status/1184359228284129280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falvinllum%2Fstatus%2F1184359228284129280&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=e0e06c01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falvinllum%2Fstatus%2F1184359228284129280&h=33877b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/alvinllum/status/1184359228284129280</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeqVtRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeqVtRk.jpg&h=1c6b19d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥一月八日上午出席行政會議前會見傳媒的答問內容（節錄）：<br />\n在按揭成數，我聽到很多意見說「供得起」但沒有首期，但大家可以想像，現在所謂「供得起」，如果按我們一貫的說法，就是那個affordability ratio，即可負擔供樓的比率，已經去到百分之七十幾。這個只是在他只借七成來供樓，<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果你說放寬給他們借更多，那可能他們供樓的負擔亦會更加大</span>。更重要的是信息發放的考慮，因為香港的樓市是非常非常敏感的，所以在信息發放方面，如果讓市民感覺到政府現在很擔心樓市調整、又可能會做一些措施，可能並不是一件很理想的事，所以這個特區政府會極度審慎來考慮。我留意到財政司司長其實都是這樣說，他舉了一連串他會考慮的因素，才會進入作出一個調整的考慮，譬如不會影響銀行體系的穩健、不會為樓市火上加油、要看私樓的供應和樓價的調整，<span style=\"color: gold;\">所以簡單來說這個議題我們未有即時的計劃</span>，亦都會極度審慎才會去移動這些有關於私人房屋現有的措施。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201901/08/P2019010800468.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F08%2FP2019010800468.htm&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=adf87442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201901/08/P2019010800468.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n好打得的林鄭今日打倒了一月的林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bae0d26d0527e16f729772d2af86a082ab61ac","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b47f578544ec199573140f1b0726baeb2c1452dc","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:47:22.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"668104f02bc974e44610e95dd62e07e2a7b2a67d","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"6ef3cf0fab9d20cd031d17c6773ecb63e7b79dbd","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"push 4"},{"pid":"0091bedc59683bb0cfb2a8fca800f2fb4b444c3c","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"push 5"},{"pid":"30835d4ab7b20c17d101e6bf5735118c513042d6","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"push 6"},{"pid":"bebbee54dbbb047414ae0ae60f3e0314f9d4ff91","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"push 7"},{"pid":"fe41d66d34c17fb599747cc451ae1c26ea491a08","tid":1657662,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f9bf3fbcea5feca89085556e5bc54a59840a8fa","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"push 8"},{"pid":"39f1c00d3c71c8155fa9f67292da632693ae9f68","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"push 9"},{"pid":"9fe0153c7f9e01066ad6a411952fbe52926b0114","tid":1657662,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,